@startuml
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Chức năng đăng nhập

actor "Người dùng" as User
boundary "_LoginScreenState" as LoginScreenState
control "AuthApiService" as AuthApiService
control "AuthController" as AuthController
control "AuthServiceImpl" as AuthServiceImpl
database "UserRepository" as UserRepository
control "PasswordEncoder" as PasswordEncoder
control "JwtUtil" as JwtUtil
control "UserMapper" as UserMapper
control "TokenStorageService" as TokenStorageService
database "SharedPreferences" as SharedPreferences
control "Navigator" as Navigator

User -> LoginScreenState: 1: nhập email, mật khẩu và bấm Đăng nhập
activate LoginScreenState

LoginScreenState -> LoginScreenState: 2: _submitLogin()
activate LoginScreenState

LoginScreenState -> AuthApiService: 3: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 4: login(LoginRequest)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> AuthController: 5: gọi API POST /auth/login
activate AuthController
AuthController -> AuthController: 6: login(LoginRequest)
activate AuthController

AuthController -> AuthServiceImpl: 7: gọi
activate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl -> AuthServiceImpl: 8: login(LoginRequest)
activate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> UserRepository: 9: gọi
activate UserRepository
UserRepository -> UserRepository: 10: findByEmailAndActive(email, true)
activate UserRepository
deactivate UserRepository
UserRepository --> AuthServiceImpl: 11: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserRepository

AuthServiceImpl -> PasswordEncoder: 12: gọi
activate PasswordEncoder
PasswordEncoder -> PasswordEncoder: 13: matches(password, passwordHash)
activate PasswordEncoder
deactivate PasswordEncoder
PasswordEncoder --> AuthServiceImpl: 14: trả về kết quả
deactivate PasswordEncoder

AuthServiceImpl -> JwtUtil: 15: gọi
activate JwtUtil
JwtUtil -> JwtUtil: 16: generateToken(User)
activate JwtUtil
deactivate JwtUtil
JwtUtil --> AuthServiceImpl: 17: trả về kết quả
deactivate JwtUtil

AuthServiceImpl -> UserMapper: 18: gọi
activate UserMapper
UserMapper -> UserMapper: 19: entityToResponse(User)
activate UserMapper
deactivate UserMapper
UserMapper --> AuthServiceImpl: 20: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserMapper

deactivate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl --> AuthController: 21: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthServiceImpl

deactivate AuthController
AuthController --> AuthApiService: 22: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> LoginScreenState: 23: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

LoginScreenState -> TokenStorageService: 24: gọi
activate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService -> TokenStorageService: 25: saveAuthSession(token, userInfo)
activate TokenStorageService

TokenStorageService -> SharedPreferences: 26: gọi
activate SharedPreferences
SharedPreferences -> SharedPreferences: 27: setString()/setInt()
activate SharedPreferences
deactivate SharedPreferences
SharedPreferences --> TokenStorageService: 28: trả về kết quả
deactivate SharedPreferences

deactivate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService --> LoginScreenState: 29: trả về kết quả
deactivate TokenStorageService

LoginScreenState -> Navigator: 30: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 31: pushNamedAndRemoveUntil()
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> LoginScreenState: 32: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate LoginScreenState

LoginScreenState --> User: 33: điều hướng đến màn hình chính
deactivate LoginScreenState

@enduml
